<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Sign up</title>
		<link
			href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
			rel="stylesheet"
			integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style3.css" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="main-title">Sign up</div>
		<div class="warning">
			新しいユーザー名とパスワードを入力してください（9文字以上）
		</div>
		<form action="/register" method="post">
			<div>
				<div>
					<div>Username</div>
					<div>Password</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<div>
						<input type="text" name="username" />
					</div>
					<div>
						<input type="password" name="password" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="error"><%= messages.error %></div>
			<div>
				<button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger" id="register">
					Sign up!
				</button>
			</div>
		</form>
		<form action="/login" method="GET">
			<div>ログインはこちら</div>
			<div>
				<button type="submit" class="btn btn-info" id="login">Login!</button>
			</div>
		</form>
	</body>
</html>
